      <dt class="news-tit ellipsis" data-level=""><a target="_blank" href="https://news.sina.com.cn/o/2019-08-20/doc-ihytcitn0552065.shtml">谢觉哉：人民司法制度的奠基者之一</a></dt>
	  
      
      <dd class="new-info">
      <div class="labels col2"><span class="date">新华网</span> | <span class="time">2019年08月20日 15:00</span></div>
      <div class="oper"><a href="http://comment5.news.sina.com.cn/comment/skin/default.html?channel=gn&newsid=comos-hytcitn0552065" target="_blank" class="review col2"><i class="CC-icon-review"></i><span class="num" cmnt_id="gn:comos-hytcitn0552065:0" name="cmnt_count"></span></a></div>        
